{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "bookName": "2 Nephi",
  "chapter": 33,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "iJpuSZDxZSBJHFSeavba",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "sister-m"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 70.068,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 0.5,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, cannot write all the things which were taught among my people;",
      "verse": "33:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 0.68,
      "end": 1.18,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither am I mighty in writing,",
      "verse": "33:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 1.36,
      "end": 1.86,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "like unto speaking;",
      "verse": "33:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 2.04,
      "end": 2.54,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for when a man speaketh by the power of the Holy Ghost",
      "verse": "33:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 2.72,
      "end": 3.22,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the power of the Holy Ghost carrieth it unto the hearts of the children of men.",
      "verse": "33:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 3.9,
      "end": 4.4,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, there are many that harden their hearts against the Holy Spirit,",
      "verse": "33:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 4.58,
      "end": 5.08,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it hath no place in them;",
      "verse": "33:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 5.26,
      "end": 5.76,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they cast many things away which are written",
      "verse": "33:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 5.94,
      "end": 6.44,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and esteem them as things of naught.",
      "verse": "33:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 7.12,
      "end": 7.62,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But I, Nephi, have written what I have written,",
      "verse": "33:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 7.8,
      "end": 8.3,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I esteem it as of great worth,",
      "verse": "33:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 8.48,
      "end": 8.98,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and especially unto my people.",
      "verse": "33:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 9.16,
      "end": 9.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For I pray continually for them by day,",
      "verse": "33:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 9.84,
      "end": 10.34,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and mine eyes water my pillow by night, because of them;",
      "verse": "33:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 10.52,
      "end": 11.02,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I cry unto my God in faith,",
      "verse": "33:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 11.2,
      "end": 11.7,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I know that he will hear my cry.",
      "verse": "33:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 12.38,
      "end": 12.88,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I know that the Lord God will consecrate my prayers",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 13.06,
      "end": 13.56,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the gain of my people.",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 13.74,
      "end": 14.24,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the words which I have written in weakness",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 14.42,
      "end": 14.92,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "will be made strong unto them;",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 15.1,
      "end": 15.6,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for it persuadeth them to do good;",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 15.78,
      "end": 16.28,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it maketh known unto them of their fathers;",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 16.46,
      "end": 16.96,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it speaketh of Jesus,",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 17.14,
      "end": 17.64,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and persuadeth them to believe in him,",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 17.82,
      "end": 18.32,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to endure to the end,",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 18.5,
      "end": 19.0,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is life eternal.",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 19.68,
      "end": 20.18,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it speaketh harshly against sin,",
      "verse": "33:5",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 20.36,
      "end": 20.86,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the plainness of the truth;",
      "verse": "33:5",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 21.04,
      "end": 21.54,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, no man will be angry at the words which I have written",
      "verse": "33:5",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 21.72,
      "end": 22.22,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save he shall be of the spirit of the devil.",
      "verse": "33:5",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 22.9,
      "end": 23.4,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I glory in plainness;",
      "verse": "33:6",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 23.58,
      "end": 24.08,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I glory in truth;",
      "verse": "33:6",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 24.26,
      "end": 24.76,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I glory in my Jesus,",
      "verse": "33:6",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 24.94,
      "end": 25.44,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he hath redeemed my soul from hell.",
      "verse": "33:6",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 26.12,
      "end": 26.62,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have charity for my people,",
      "verse": "33:7",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 26.8,
      "end": 27.3,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and great faith in Christ",
      "verse": "33:7",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 27.48,
      "end": 27.98,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I shall meet many souls spotless at his judgment-seat.",
      "verse": "33:7",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 28.66,
      "end": 29.16,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have charity for the Jew\u2014",
      "verse": "33:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 29.34,
      "end": 29.84,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I say Jew, because I mean them from whence I came.",
      "verse": "33:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 30.52,
      "end": 31.02,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I also have charity for the Gentiles.",
      "verse": "33:9",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 31.2,
      "end": 31.7,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, for none of these can I hope",
      "verse": "33:9",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 31.88,
      "end": 32.38,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "except they shall be reconciled unto Christ,",
      "verse": "33:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 32.56,
      "end": 33.06,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and enter into the narrow gate,",
      "verse": "33:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 33.24,
      "end": 33.74,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and walk in the strait path which leads to life,",
      "verse": "33:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 33.92,
      "end": 34.42,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and continue in the path",
      "verse": "33:9",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 34.6,
      "end": 35.1,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until the end of the day of probation.",
      "verse": "33:9",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 35.78,
      "end": 37.823,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 38.003,
      "end": 38.503,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also Jew,",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 38.683,
      "end": 39.183,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all ye ends of the earth,",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 39.363,
      "end": 39.863,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "hearken unto these words and believe in Christ;",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 40.043,
      "end": 40.543,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and if ye believe not in these words believe in Christ.",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 40.723,
      "end": 41.223,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if ye shall believe in Christ",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 41.403,
      "end": 41.903,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye will believe in these words,",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 42.083,
      "end": 42.583,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they are the words of Christ,",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 42.763,
      "end": 43.263,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he hath given them unto me;",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 43.443,
      "end": 43.943,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they teach all men that they should do good.",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 44.623,
      "end": 45.123,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if they are not the words of Christ,",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 45.303,
      "end": 45.803,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "judge ye\u2014",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 45.983,
      "end": 46.483,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for Christ will show unto you,",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 46.663,
      "end": 47.163,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with power and great glory,",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 47.343,
      "end": 47.843,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they are his words,",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 48.023,
      "end": 48.523,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "at the last day;",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 48.703,
      "end": 49.203,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and you and I shall stand face to face before his bar;",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 49.383,
      "end": 49.883,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and ye shall know that I have been commanded of him",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 50.063,
      "end": 50.563,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to write these things,",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 50.743,
      "end": 51.243,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "notwithstanding my weakness.",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 51.923,
      "end": 52.423,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I pray the Father in the name of Christ",
      "verse": "33:12",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 52.603,
      "end": 53.103,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that many of us,",
      "verse": "33:12",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 53.283,
      "end": 53.783,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if not all,",
      "verse": "33:12",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 53.963,
      "end": 54.463,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "may be saved in his kingdom",
      "verse": "33:12",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 54.643,
      "end": 55.143,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "at that great and last day.",
      "verse": "33:12",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 55.823,
      "end": 57.866,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "33:13",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 58.046,
      "end": 58.546,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "all those who are of the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "33:13",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 58.726,
      "end": 59.226,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all ye ends of the earth,",
      "verse": "33:13",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 59.406,
      "end": 59.906,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I speak unto you as the voice of one crying from the dust:",
      "verse": "33:13",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 60.086,
      "end": 60.586,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Farewell until that great day shall come.",
      "verse": "33:13",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 61.266,
      "end": 61.766,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And you that will not partake of the goodness of God,",
      "verse": "33:14",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 61.946,
      "end": 62.446,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and respect the words of the Jews,",
      "verse": "33:14",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 62.626,
      "end": 63.126,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also my words,",
      "verse": "33:14",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 63.306,
      "end": 63.806,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the words which shall proceed forth out of the mouth of the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "33:14",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 63.986,
      "end": 64.486,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, I bid you an everlasting farewell,",
      "verse": "33:14",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 64.666,
      "end": 65.166,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for these words shall condemn you at the last day.",
      "verse": "33:14",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 65.846,
      "end": 66.346,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For what I seal on earth,",
      "verse": "33:15",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 66.526,
      "end": 67.026,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be brought against you at the judgment bar;",
      "verse": "33:15",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 67.206,
      "end": 67.706,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for thus hath the Lord commanded me,",
      "verse": "33:15",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 67.886,
      "end": 68.386,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I must obey.",
      "verse": "33:15",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 68.566,
      "end": 69.402,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "33:15",
      "lineIndex": 89
    }
  ]
}